---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '../../i18n/ui';

const lang = 'en' as const;
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<BaseLayout lang={lang} title={t('about.title')}>
  <h1>{t('about.title')}</h1>
  <p>
    This site focuses on <strong>HCL Domino</strong> and its broader ecosystem (Notes, Domino REST
    API, Volt MX, Nomad, AppDev Pack, and more) — covering the latest news and technical articles.
  </p>
  <p>
    A daily GitHub Actions cron triggers the publishing flow:
    <strong>OpenAI GPT drafts the article</strong> →
    <strong>Anthropic Claude cross-reviews it</strong> (to reduce single-model
    bias and hallucination; critical factual issues block publication and force
    a rewrite) → <strong>the consultant adds hands-on context and corrections</strong>.
    Topics are drawn from the last 24–72 hours of official HCL announcements,
    HCL Ambassador blogs, and OpenNTF activity — when there's no news on a
    given day, the post is a deep-dive on an under-covered class or feature
    from the official docs instead. Every source is cited at the end of the post.
  </p>
  <p>
    Traditional Chinese and English versions are published together. The
    two-model review plus human checkpoint exists specifically to catch the
    failure modes typical of pure AI content — factual mistakes, hallucinated
    API names, and miscited sources. Source code and the full workflow are
    open on <a href="https://github.com/bryanHsiao/domino-news">GitHub</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
